reviews.review_text: This BK has decent numbers of sitting and tables for different group sizes. There is patio area as well. Food and cleaning was good. Staff should be more frindly. Location is at the corner of Kingsway and Hall then roadside parking are metered unless you park in the behind streets for 30 min or 2 hours free spots.
The restaurant is always kept clean. The team members have a welcoming smile and are very humble. Their menu range is very vast and u get a lot to chose from. Definitely give it a try

Good and fresh food. Staff is nice and friendly. Had crispy chicken combo which was quite good. Overall nice experience, will return soon. Vegetarian options: They had veggie burgers and plant based whoppers. Kid-friendliness: Got some nice deals for kids menu.
Today I get spicy chicken and veggie burger good in taste . The staff was so friendly. The store is neat and clean.
What can I say, other than a whopper is my favourite burger. I went there on my birthday as I wanted this burger.
Always get fresh food with great amount of ingredients. Really caring and helpful staff. Thanks for serving us.
The taste of the burgers are very nice and juicy, has a unique taste , also love their milkshakes    and veggie burgers wow      delicious ..
All good except parking is not easy. Good things are, always not crowded, the crews are always kind and never forget ketchup for fries. Food
I visit this place regularly and they provide good quality of food and service.
I get Whoppers here and they are always great. Friendly service, but sometimes I wish it was a bit quicker when theyre busy. Clean premisis with friendly employees and great fast-food.
Had the best customer service today from aehaas. Woud come back to this location.
Excellent eating experience.. from walking in the door and being greeted by employee, Meal was served hot and excellent taste. Employee was very friendly and helpful.
The best Burger King I ever visit. Friendly staff , great deals . The interior is so good  that I enjoyed every minute there . The quality and quantity was great too .
Everytime Ive been here its been fantastic service. The place is not quite as clean as it could be, but the food tastes better than McDonalds

Great place for families, service is very good, attendants very nice, a bit slow during peak hours (we visited around dinner), the place is clean and beautiful, food was great, price tag is fair, there are lots of sides to add to your order. Definitely recommended for groups and families (as soon as the pandemic allows, for the time being only a few tables are open for dine-in(

Honestly, I used to really hate Burger King after getting a really bad whopper at the Calgary airport. This place has made me a BK Stan after eating a South Western Chicken Sandwich with onion rings and Oreo shake. Their South Western beef burgers are pretty good and have a nice smokey flavor to them too. I am an avid McDonalds lover but their shakes are awful and their burgers look pathetic, but not the Kings.
A bit slow when busy and under-staffed but they survive despite competitors very close by.  Food quality always good.  Service pleasant. Indoor dining kept tidy.

Of all the fast food deals available these days the best is 2 Whoppers for $8. A delicious burger that tastes like you made it at home. Far better than Wendys, A & W and McDs. The nugget special if 10 for $2.99 is also delicious. Real chicken and yummy.
The store is really neat and clean. Being on the busiest location, still they manages to serve quickly and quality food. Surely returning here in future. Best on kingsway.
We think Burger Kings burgers are bigger and better than McDonalds.  Use their APP to have a lot of great deals!

It was the bestest experience so far at burger king kingsway I didnt know about the deals when I was having trouble for deciding they helped with sharing the deals details and I could not resist my self to buy 4 king meal deals and as soon as I made payment my order was ready I was so happy seeing that .the staff is so nice and well behaved !!
Quiet location! Staff was great!!  Burgers delicious as always!!

Its not always the fastest, but it is the freshest. Not sure what they do differently, but the veggies are crispier, the meat is more frilly and not as fasty foody. I cant explain, but as a person whos frequented BK a lot, and at one point went for Whopper Wednesday 40x in one year, this is one of the best ones.

Dont feel strange when you find it slightly empty. Mcdonalds is 20 steps away from it and as for the highgate villiage area...which is not as dense like granville street for instance,...and the nature of it is different, this emptyness makes sense, it is in a very bad geographical location. But the service is great...nothing unusual about the food or place.

I like this Burger King for 3 reasons - Inside is very bright with high ceilings and also the seats makes there a cozy place. - Staff is very friendly They make the best Whoppers. You might say whopper is the same in every Burger King. No, my friend, no  For example the Burger King in metrotown don t have jalapeno option. Moreover juicyness of the whopper is perfect here

Home of whoppers especially this location is very well maintained and clean I went there in the evening there was a huge line up over there despite of only 3 people working over there they managed it very well the person named Sam working as a cashier was very polite and respectful and handled very thing properly. Moreover the food was also superb...
I wish they had drive-thru service. Good taste. I like BK promotions, always making it great deals.
Great Burgers and pies there milkshakes are great nice polite and faster than Micky Ds Parking: Sorry dont know Wheelchair accessibility: Side door easy access via scooters ect.
Ahhh great deals in town .. one should try impossible whopper and I find this place so clean and service is so fast even though they are really busy     delicious food
Best burgers. Always make fresh. Very delicious. Friendly staff. Quick service. Just wow
really nice staff and love their service. manager was really polite and she was so friendly with her staff and customer. best fast food restaurant and fantastic staff.
I love this place great food and great service     store is so clean and they follow all covid protocols and service was really quick   moreover great deal like 2 for $6 and 2 for $8

Very nice bunch of people that work there like everyone theyre under pressure with the covid so we just try to be be patient with the other customers that are so so rude to these nice people but I give him five stars they work hard !
Very good
Hello Im yusof today I went to burger   King and  the employe gave me and my brother free milkshakes it was really good experience thanks burger King
Employee girl Preet has excellent customer service skills ..she notified me about good deal.She should be rewarded with raise.food was nice too..
Very polite and friendly staff.food was served fresh and hot. Highly satisfying experience.
Wowwwww great place in town and service is so fast and they are always busy ..... good job everyone you make my day more gratefull

Ate me a burger, or was surprisingly great, really glad I didnt go to mcdicks for a mediocre meal.

The owner is nice cooks the food as you wait.none of the food sits under a light
